Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and symbolic representation of the concept of God's existence, blending elements of light and darkness. Depict a celestial figure surrounded by rays of light, casting a glow of divinity upon a world shrouded in shadows. Symbolize the eternal presence and power of God amidst the uncertainties and doubts of humanity. Incorporate subtle biblical motifs such as a dove representing the Holy Spirit or a lamb symbolizing sacrifice and redemption. Capture the essence of spiritual contemplation and faith through a visually striking and thought-provoking composition.
